This file contains the step by step installation process.

System Requirement:-

1.Any linux operating system preferably Ubuntu 18.04 (tested only on ubuntu 18.04 by me itself).
2.Gcc compiler should be installed onto the system which every developer probably must have (for editing the source code).(developers only)
3.Any text editor (for editing source code).(developers only)

Installation Steps:-

1.Download or Clone the project repository onto your system.
2.Now your software is downloaded.
3.Navigate to the folder with the help of command line.
4.Change your directory to bin.
5.Enter this command ./start_page
6.Your library management system will start on running.

For more information read the README file and for using this project for your purpose read the licence file.
